FOR SERVER:
===========

1) Go to Project Directory
2) Create "storage" directory
3) sqlite3 database.db < create_database.sql
2) virtualenv venv
3) source venv/bin/activate
4) pip install Flask
5) python server.py


FOR CLIENT:
===========

1) Go to Project Directory
2) virtualenv venv
3) source venv/bin/activate
4) pip install Watchdog
5) pip install requests
6) python client.py
